cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with image-based shape generation and deep learning-based shape reconstruction, which are primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of conditional generative networks and differentiable guidance also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the experimental results and ablation studies involve the evaluation of 3D reconstruction, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
